  Locus:
    Page: 179
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Friendship
---
So-called friends are in reality enemies. You will not find in this whole
universe a single friend without egotism. Your true friend in need, He who
is sincerely attached to you, is God, who lives within your heart.
